sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User (Browser)
    participant FB as Firebase Auth
    participant FE as React Frontend
    participant NG as Nginx Proxy
    participant BE as Express Backend
    participant DB as MySQL

    Note over U,DB: Email/Password Login Flow
    U->>FE: Enter email + password
    FE->>NG: POST /api/auth/login
    NG->>BE: Proxy to backend:5000
    BE->>DB: Find user by email
    DB-->>BE: User record (with passwordHash)
    BE->>BE: bcrypt.compare(password, hash)
    BE->>BE: generateAccessToken(JWT)
    BE->>DB: Store RefreshToken
    BE-->>NG: { user, token, refreshToken }
    NG-->>FE: Response
    FE->>FE: localStorage.setItem("chronicles-token", token)
    FE-->>U: Redirect to Dashboard

    Note over U,DB: Social Login Flow (Google/GitHub)
    U->>FB: signInWithPopup(provider)
    FB-->>U: Firebase ID Token
    U->>FE: ID Token received
    FE->>NG: POST /api/auth/social { idToken }
    NG->>BE: Proxy to backend:5000
    BE->>FB: firebaseAdmin.auth().verifyIdToken(idToken)
    FB-->>BE: Decoded Token (uid, email, provider)
    BE->>DB: Find or Create AuthIdentity + User
    DB-->>BE: User record
    BE->>BE: generateAccessToken(JWT)
    BE->>DB: Store RefreshToken
    BE-->>NG: { user, token, refreshToken }
    NG-->>FE: Response
    FE->>FE: localStorage.setItem("chronicles-token", token)
    FE-->>U: Redirect to Dashboard
